        <abstract> 
<p>Sends Asa Gray’s review [of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>]. Asks THH’s advice on getting it reprinted in England.</p> 
            <p>Hooker’s expedition to Syria.</p> 
<p>Disgraceful review of Tyndall’s book in <hi rend="italic">Athenæum</hi>.</p> 
